data.description: *MULTIPLE OFFERS RECEIVED. OFFER DEADLINE 4/12 AT 4PM* Welcome to your dream home! This stunning 4-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom residence embodies modern elegance and comfort. Nestled in a peaceful neighborhood, this home has a beautiful kitchen with granite countertops, sleek stainless-steel appliances, a kitchen island, and a spacious family room. You will have the ease of a first-floor laundry, a 2-car attached garage w/remote, and an abundance of natural light. Upstairs, you will find four generously sized bedrooms. The primary bedroom has a walk-in closet, sitting area, vaulted ceilings, and a double sink ensuite. The basement is insulated and prepped for finishing. Outside, the expansive backyard provides the perfect setting for outdoor gatherings on the patio, which offers a sliding door leading to the home. This lovely home will not last; schedule your showing today!  * Mounted TVs & Electric Fireplace are excluded but can be purchased separately. *
